me.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/liam-payne@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/liam-payne@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/liam-payne@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/liam-payne@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，一组法官否认，在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-payne">利亚姆·佩恩（Liam Payne</a> ）死亡的情况下，最近宣布了罗杰·诺雷斯（Roger Nores）和两名酒店工作人员的无罪释放的上诉。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/liam-payne-one-direction-obituary-3803755">Liam Payne 1993-2024：帮助引发流行现象的单向明星</a></strong></li></ul><p>佩恩（Payne）<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-directions-liam-payne-had-died-aged-31-3803523">在阿根廷布宜诺斯艾利斯（Buenos Aires）的卡萨苏尔·巴勒莫（Casasur Palermo）酒店的三楼阳台上发生致命降落</a>后，可悲的是去年10月16日死亡。阿根廷检察官办公室透露，这位31岁的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-cause-of-death-and-details-of-hotel-room-in-disarray-revealed-3803859">死亡原因是由于多次创伤以及内部和外部出血</a>。</p><p>佩恩（Payne）去世后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/five-people-charged-in-connection-with-death-of-liam-payne-3825247">五人被捕并被指控与他的死有关</a>。在被捕的人中，有歌手的朋友罗杰·诺雷斯（Roger Nores）和两名Casasur Palermo Hotel Gilda Martin和Esteban Grassi的员工。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-friend-hotel-workers-exonerated-from-negligent-homicide-manslaughter-charges-3839651">今年早些时候，这三个人都被免除了所有指控</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3829687" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3829687" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3829687" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Liam-Payne-Photo-by-Slaven-Vlasic_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="利亚姆·佩恩" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Liam-Payne-Photo-by-Slaven-Vlasic_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Liam-Payne-Photo-by-Slaven-Vlasic_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Liam-Payne-Photo-by-Slaven-Vlasic_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Liam-Payne-Photo-by-Slaven-Vlasic_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Liam-Payne-Photo-by-Slaven-Vlasic_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Liam-Payne-Photo-by-Slaven-Vlasic_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3829687" class="wp-caption-text">利亚姆·佩恩（Liam Payne） - 信用：Slaven Vlasic/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>现在，根据一份<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/liam-payne-death-appeal-acquittal-denied-1235295777/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石</em></a>报告，向寻求诺雷斯的上诉，马丁和格拉西被推翻的无罪释放被提交给一组法官小组，后者裁定否认这一点。</p><p>根据<em>滚石公司的</em>说法，上诉是在3月5日提起的，并辩称，将三名被告嫌疑人的法官赋予了“推理中有缺陷”，并且该案中的某些信息和证据在无罪释放时尚未进行审查。</p><p>但是，法官小组正在坚决支持他们的免除，对每<em>卷石头</em>做出了回应：“与其对法院推理的具体详细的批评，不仅仅是对所收集的证据的评估，反复说明了对进一步行动的需求，而是在法院指出的那样，“这两个党派都提出了任何相关行动，这都否认了这一相关行动。” </p><figure id="attachment_3823942" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3823942" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3823942" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Stephane-Cardinale-Corbis_Corbis-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Stephane-Cardinale-Corbis_Corbis-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Stephane-Cardinale-Corbis_Corbis-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Stephane-Cardinale-Corbis_Corbis-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Stephane-Cardinale-Corbis_Corbis-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Stephane-Cardinale-Corbis_Corbis-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Liam-Payne.-CREDIT_-Stephane-Cardinale-Corbis_Corbis-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3823942" class="wp-caption-text">利亚姆·佩恩。图片来源：Stephane Cardinale  -  Corbis/Corbis通过Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>因此，法官得出的结论是，上诉“缺乏继续进行的必要优点”。据报道，提起上诉的检察官现在<a href="https://www.fiscales.gob.ar/fiscalias/caso-liam-payne-el-mpf-recurrio-en-distintas-instancias-los-sobreseimientos-de-tres-imputados/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">将其案件提交给最高法院CámaraDeCasación</a>以进行进一步审查。</p><p>在佩恩（Payne）死亡的五名原始嫌疑人中，剩下的两名人员 - 埃兹奎尔·佩雷拉（Ezequiel Pereyra）和布拉伊安·帕兹（Braian Paiz）在等待审判时将留在监狱中。对于他们的两个部分， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/police-arrest-two-people-in-connection-with-death-of-liam-payne-3810706">Pereyra和Paiz都被指控用毒品吸收Payne</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-payne-reportedly-had-pink-cocaine-and-other-substances-in-his-system-at-time-of-death-3804922">其中一些是在死后毒理学报告后在他的体内发现的</a>。</p><p> 11月，帕兹（Paiz）打破了沉默，承认他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/suspect-in-liam-payne-death-investigation-breaks-silence-3811500">在去世前两次遇到了后来的单向方向，并承认与他一起吸毒</a>。但是，他坚持认为他从未为佩恩提供麻醉品，也没有接受他的任何钱。如果被判有罪，Paiz和Pereyra都可能面临四到15年的监禁。据报道，Paiz还必须支付4,900美元的罚款。 </p><figure id="attachment_3820944" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3820944" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3820944" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/LiamPayne@2000x1270.jpg" alt="利亚姆·佩恩（Liam Payne）在2018年现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/LiamPayne@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/LiamPayne@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/LiamPayne@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/LiamPayne@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/LiamPayne@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/LiamPayne@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3820944" class="wp-caption-text">利亚姆·佩恩（Liam Payne）在2018年进行现场表演。荣誉：汉娜·拉森（Hanna Lassen）/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>一月份， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-cause-of-death-and-details-of-final-moments-confirmed-in-uk-inquest-3827282">在白金汉郡验尸官法院的一次听证会证实，佩恩的死是“ Polytrauma”的结果，</a>这是指人体器官系统遭受的多次创伤性伤害。</p><p>在其他地方，佩恩（Payne）的朋友<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-friend-roger-nores-sues-late-one-direction-stars-father-for-defamation-3829685">罗杰·诺雷斯（Roger Nores）最近对已故明星的父亲杰夫（Geoff）提起了联邦诽谤诉讼，要求其诽谤</a>。</p><p>邮政<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/judges-deny-appeal-to-overturn-acquittal-of-liam-paynes-friend-and-hotel-workers-in-death-investigation-3846193">法官否认对Liam Payne的朋友和酒店工作人员死亡调查的无罪释放的上诉</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
